keywords pdelete
---
Syntax: pdelete <password>

Permanently deletes your player character.  Your save file is removed and your
connection is closed immediately.  This action cannot be undone.

You must supply your current password to confirm the deletion.  A wrong
password imposes a 10-second wait before you can try again.

If your account has no password set, the command may be used without an
argument.
